short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Insert JavaScript Libraries Into Your Console

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Provides a drop-down list of javascript libraries you can load into your browser.  Just click the extension icon, select a library, and... boom!  The library is loaded into your browser and available to play around with in your console.  
  
Feedback and Contributions are welcome!  https://github.com/jxm262/consoletap
